    "collapsible_content_TBcQ3p": {
      "type": "collapsible-content",
      "blocks": {
        "collapsible_tab_3zc4JQ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "1. What is the suction power of a cordless vacuum cleaner? How many Pa is considered strong?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The suction power of a cordless vacuum cleaner generally ranges from <strong>18,000Pa to 30,000Pa<\/strong>，The suction force that can reach 20000pa is very strong. <a href=\"\/products\/p7-pro-cordless-vacuum\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"【New Arrival】Honiture P7 Pro Cordless Vacuum\">Honiture P7 Pro<\/a> Can reach 50000Pa clean pet hair.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_6QFNj4": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "2. What is the battery life? Is it sufficient for cleaning large apartments?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Cordless vacuum cleaners typically have a battery life of <strong>30–60 minutes<\/strong>.honiture's cordless vacuum cleaners can last more than 55 minutes in standard conditions.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_cATyNQ": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "3. Is a vacuum cleaner noisy? Will using it affect my hearing?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>The noise level of mainstream cordless vacuum cleaners on the market is generally between 70-85 decibels.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_Xtm4U6": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "4. How is the filtration system? Is it friendly for people with pets or allergies?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>Honiture vacuum cleaners are equipped with a <strong>high-efficiency HEPA filtration system and a fully sealed<\/strong> design to prevent secondary pollution and provide a healthier living environment for your family. For example, <a href=\"https:\/\/honiture.com\/products\/p7-pro-cordless-vacuum\/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/honiture.com\/products\/p7-pro-cordless-vacuum\/\">Honiture P7 Pro<\/a> uses 7layer hapa filtration system.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        },
        "collapsible_tab_j8xn8H": {
          "type": "collapsible_tab",
          "settings": {
            "heading": "5. Is the vacuum cleaner heavy? Is it difficult to use?",
            "open": false,
            "content": "<p>No, vacuum cleaners weighing around 2.5-3 kg are a common weight on the market, and usually have more balanced performance and battery life.<\/p>",
            "page": "",
            "custom_liquid": ""
          }
        }
      },
